<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَاجْمَعْ عَلَى تَحْرِيمِهَا النَّاسُ كُلُّهُمْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَكَفِرْ مُبِيحِيهَا وَفِي النَّارِ خَلِّدِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَإِدْمَانِهَا إِحْدَى الْكَبَائِرِ فَاجْتَنِبْ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَعَلَّكَ تُحْظَى بِالْفَلاحِ وَتَهْتَدِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَيَحْرُمُ مِنْهَا النَّزْرُ مِثْلَ كَثِيرِهَا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>ولَيْسَتْ دَاوَءً بِلْ هِيَ الدَّاءُ فَابْعِدِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَمَا جَعَلَ اللهُ الْعَظِيمَ دَوَاءَنَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>بِمَا هُوَ مَحْظُورٌ بِمِلَّةِ أَحْمَدِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَكُلُّ شَرَابٍ إِنْ تَكَاثَرَ مُسْكِرٌ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>يُحَرَّمُ مِنْهُ النَّزْرُ بِالْخَمْرِ فَاعْدِدِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَمِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ كَانَ يَحْرُمُ مُطْلَقًا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَلَوْ كَانَ مَطْبُوخًا بِغَيْرِ تَقَيُّدِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَسِيَّانَ مِنْ بُرٍّ وَمِنْ ذُرَةٍ وَمِنْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>شَعِيرٍ وَتَمْرٍ أَيْ وَكُلِّ مُعَوَّدِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>سِوَى لِظَمَا الْمُضْطَّرِ إِنْ مُزِجَتْ بِمَا<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>يُرَوِّي وَلِلْمُغْتَصِّ إجْمَاعًا ازْرُدِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ثَمَانِينَ فَاجْلِدْ مُسْلِمًا شَارِبًا رِضَى<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>عَلَيْهَا بِاسْكَارِ الْكَثِيرِ الْمُزَبِّدِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>وَمَنْ مَاتَ فِي حَدٍّ بِغَيْرِ تَزَيُّدٍ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَلا غُرْمَ فِيهِ وَلْيُغَسَّلْ وَيُلْحَدِ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>موعظة<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>عباد الله إن مفتاح سعادة المرء في دنياه وأخراه أن يراقب مولاه<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>